/**
 * Dev-mode fixtures. Used when pywebview is not available (vite dev in browser).
 *
 * NOT the source of truth — that's `glassbox/fixtures/*.json`, generated by
 * running sisa.py with varied configs. These ts fixtures mirror that output
 * shape and are kept thin on purpose: real numbers will replace them at T-2h.
 */
